# Normalize all text to LF in the repo and check out LF on every OS.
# Critical: the bash hooks + statusline must stay LF - CRLF breaks Git-Bash on
# Windows clones (`/bin/bash^M: bad interpreter`). Default git autocrlf=true on
# Windows would otherwise re-mangle them on every fresh clone.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Belt-and-suspenders for the executable shell scripts.
*.sh text eol=lf
